    <h3><em>Seated Woman Holding Mirror</em>, Tang dynasty (A.D. 618–907), first half of 8th century</h3>

    <p>
    Earthenware with three-color (sancai) lead glazes and traces of polychrome pigments<br />    31.2 x 13.8 x 15.5 cm (12.3 x 5.4 x 6.1 in.)<br />        Gift of Pauline Palmer Wood, 1970.1075</p>
        
